name: Fitness Finda
overview: Fitness Finda is an Australian company providing a web-based portal that helps connect fitness-minded individuals with providers of various exercise opportunities. Fitness Finda’s site is community driven. Local gyms and personal trainers across Australia have the opportunity to list their services on the site, and consumers can post their comments and reviews. The site is easy to navigate, allowing users to perform a simple postcode search, or else search within given fitness categories and then drill down by state and city to find the resources closest to them. Everything from Zumba classes to running groups to specialised gyms and personal training services can be found on Fitness Finda. Fitness Finda is dedicated to keeping users interested in fitness and motivated to meet their fitness goals. They provide links to bargain fitness accessories and equipment through a fitness deals tab, while their blog covers a wide range of topics of interest to both hard-core fitness enthusiasts and casual exercisers. Gyms and personal trainers can choose from a free basic listing or a paid listing complete with marketing services including featured status and the ability to advertise deals on Fitness Finda, plus assistance with phone number tracking and custom Google ad campaigns.
